# Getting started with Pushover

To use any of the modules below, you need to connect your Pushover account to Integromat. If you do not have a Pushover account yet, you can create one at [Pushover.com](https://pushover.net/login).

## Connecting the Pushover service to Integromat

To connect your Pushover account to Integromat, follow the general instructions for [Connecting to services](https://support.integromat.com/hc/en-us/articles/360001990194#create-a-connection). When creating a scenario, you will be asked to provide an API key. To get your API key, login to your Pushover account (https://pushover.net/login) where you can see Your User Key.



Copy Your User Key and paste it into Integromat. Now you can continue and finish your scenario.
